content.html:
Twice-divorced Loose Women presenter Coleen Nolan longs to find love again and craves romance but is insecure about her age and her looks. Ashley Banjo pairs her with project manager Kevin, who is also divorced, creating a sensual and romantic dance in the picturesque grounds of a manor house. Made in Chelsea star Miles Nazaire is matched with foodie and fitness vlogger Steph, who is looking for someone to share her fast-paced life with. Ashley choreographs a dance full of passionate moves, risky lifts, and racy eye contact, taking place at the historic Rivoli Ballroom in south London.
